com.siperian.bdd.userexits.operations

Interface ITaskOperationPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBaseOperationPlugin, ISaveOperationPlugin

    public interface ITaskOperationPlugin
extends ISaveOperationPlugin

    Defines the user exits for the Task operations.

    All Task operations are extensions of the save operation, The difference is that the user exits need to know about the context of the task being performed. Additional OperationContext properties are defined.

    Should have TASK_ACTION_OPERATION operation type
